able to see their property 
bill and audrey wyatt said theyve had it with life in the flood 
plain though theyll keep their camilla twin harbors property as a 
vacation getaway they bought their trailer last year right before 
the june flood 
we dont want to give up the place but i dont want to live 
here any more weve been through this twice in one year mrs 
