the bankdispensed stamp harry zelenko of new york city designed 
it 
the ultimate goal is to develop a similar stamp made of 
recyclable paper frank said 
at fridays ceremony in seattles columbiaseafirst tower 
people lined up to buy firstday covers the festivities also 
