<TEXT>
fear of taxes is rising and with plenty of 
reason 
the tax foundation states that each americans share of the 
federal debt will increase by 827 in fiscal year 1991 and doesnt 
everyone know that debts eventually have to be paid or somehow 
worked off 
take your eye off taxes and they rise 
